Usage: merge_pg_library [-help] [-force <string>] -library_list_file <string>
                        [-library_prefix <string>]
                        [-merge_ddv_currents <string>]
                        [-merge_single_voltage_pgvs <string>] [-output <string>]
                        [-remove_tech <string>] [-validate_rail_merge <string>]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
-force <string>                         # <true|false> (string, optional)
-library_list_file <string>             # <absolute library path>
                                        # (string, required)
-library_prefix <string>                # <prefix> (string, optional)
-merge_ddv_currents <string>            # <true|false> (string, optional)
-merge_single_voltage_pgvs <string>     # <true|false> (string, optional)
-output <string>                        # <directory name> (string, optional)
-remove_tech <string>                   # <true|false> (string, optional)
-validate_rail_merge <string>           # <true|false> (string, optional)